(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

37:27.329 --> 37:29.160
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

37:29.540 --> 37:31.531
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

37:39.800 --> 37:41.756
All right, Carp. I'm in.

37:41.844 --> 37:42.833
Really?

37:42.928 --> 37:44.384
I don't know
what brand of fool
you truly are,

37:44.471 --> 37:46.848
